FORECAST FOR IRISH COASTAL WATERS FROM MALIN HEAD TO WICKLOW HEAD TO MIZEN
HEAD AND FOR THE IRISH SEA
WIND: NORTH OR NORTHWEST FORCE 5 OR 6. DECREASING FORCE 4 OR 5 IMMINENT
MAINLY BETWEEN NORTHWEST AND NORTHEAST IN DIRECTION. SOON BECOMING VARIABLE
